article_title: What Romneycare Taught Me About Obamacare

article_metadata.author: Victor Lipman

og.description: Having some brontosaurus blood in me (aka, not being the swiftest with new technology), it took me about two hours to find the website and navigate around it. But I saved myself over $2000 a year.
